  "commit_message": "[dynamo] mimic tp_richcompare handling (#182759)\n\nAdd comparison operator support to torch.compile by implementing CPython's do_richcompare / tp_richcompare dispatch on Dynamo's VariableTracker hierarchy.\n\nEach VT gets a richcompare_impl slot (analogous to tp_richcompare), and generic_richcompare implements the do_richcompare 4-step algorithm (subclass priority, forward, reflected, fallback) directly using these slots. COMPARE_OP routes through generic_richcompare; call_method(\"__eq__\") calls ri",
